text:
Producer,
What are your plans for Christmas?

...Producer,
don't you want to do something Christmassy?

Something Christmassy...
Hmm, I can't really imagine it.

Huh, really?
I definitely want to do something...

...! Is that so?
If Hanana wants it, then maybe we should give it a try.

I'll make a firm decision, so wait for me...
...a Christmas-like job...!
